---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPage.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Us"
	description="Notivra Insight — powering academic journeys with data, clarity, and craft."
	pubDate={new Date('September 24 2025')}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	<div class="space-y-8">
		<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
			<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8 text-indigo-600 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
				<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 20l9-7-9-7-9 7 9 7z" />
			</svg>
			<p>
				At Notivra Insight, we believe knowledge shouldn’t be locked behind barriers of time,
				language, or technical skill. We exist to help students, researchers, and institutions
				move from raw ideas to polished outcomes — bridging the gap between ambition and
				achievement.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
			<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8 text-green-600 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
				<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M12 2a10 10 0 100 20 10 10 0 000-20z" />
			</svg>
			<p>
				We craft more than just papers or reports; we build pathways. From complex data analysis
				to tailored academic writing, every project we take is anchored in rigor, precision, and
				a deep understanding of the academic process.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
			<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
				<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 17v-6h13v6M9 8V6a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v2m-7 0h7" />
			</svg>
			<p>
				Born in Aceh and inspired by the global challenges of conservation, science, and
				education, Notivra Insight draws from both local realities and international standards.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
			<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8 text-yellow-600 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
				<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 1.567-3 3.5S10.343 15 12 15s3-1.567 3-3.5S13.657 8 12 8z" />
				<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.341A8 8 0 1112 4v4l3 3" />
			</svg>
			<p>
				We are skeptical of shortcuts, allergic to mediocrity, and driven by the conviction that
				academic excellence is not a privilege but a craft that can be cultivated.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
			<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8 text-red-600 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
				<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6v6l4 2" />
				<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 22C6.477 22 2 17.523 2 12S6.477 2 12 2s10 4.477 10 10-4.477 10-10 10z" />
			</svg>
			<p>
				Notivra Insight is more than a service. It’s a companion for the long, often lonely, road
				of research and learning. We stand beside you — questioning, refining, and sharpening
				your work — so that when your ideas meet the world, they do so with strength, clarity,
				and impact.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>
